	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The guest is right.
<br />
<br /><span class="posthilit">PPU</span> Address updates as follows:
<br />
<br />Reload (LoopyV = LoopyT)  on cycle 304
<br />
<br />X increment (LoopyV += 1)  every 3rd cycle: 3, 11, 19, etc
<br />
<br />X reload (LoopyV &amp; 0x041F = LoopyT &amp; 0x041F)  on cycle 257
<br />
<br />Y increment (LoopyV += 0x1000, + 0x20 on <span class="posthilit">wrap</span>, xor 0x0800 on <span class="posthilit">wrap</span>)  on cycle 251
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />Above occurs on every rendered <span class="posthilit">PPU</span> scanline <em>as well as</em> the pre-render scanline as long as the <span class="posthilit">PPU</span> is on (BG or sprites enabled) at the given time  -- with the exceoption of the Address Reload, which <em>only</em> occurs on the pre-render scanline.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


